<hr>
<h2 data-heading="4. DataAdapter" dir="auto">4. DataAdapter</h2>
<h3 data-heading="Overview" dir="auto">Overview</h3>
<p dir="auto">The DataAdapter serves as a bridge between a DataSet and a data source, populating the DataSet with data and managing changes made to it.</p>
<h3 data-heading="Key Functions" dir="auto">Key Functions</h3>
<ul>
<li dir="auto">Fill: Populates a DataSet with data from the database.</li>
<li dir="auto">Update: Saves changes made in the DataSet back to the database.</li>
</ul>
