<h2 data-heading="5. DataSet" dir="auto">5. DataSet</h2>
<h3 data-heading="Overview" dir="auto">Overview</h3>
<p dir="auto">A DataSet is an in-memory representation of data that can hold multiple data tables and relationships. It is disconnected from the data source.</p>
<h3 data-heading="Key Features" dir="auto">Key Features</h3>
<ul>
<li dir="auto">Multiple Tables: Can store multiple tables and maintain relationships.</li>
